{"tid":717033,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日條女教我咩係越位","createTime":"2018-06-25T18:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T05:33:21.000Z","uid":26000,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fad149239f5a222ed45190c60d1a10af5baf65","tid":717033,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇巴打同我一樣 對足球冇乜興趣 所以做咁多年人都唔點留意足球<br />\n基本上可以話係對足球零認知<br />\n<br />\n反而條女呢 就好鍾意睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一來為𥄫仔 二來真係睇波<br />\n咁呢排世界杯 小弟原本都冇乜為意 但條女就上身咁款話要睇波<br />\n早個禮拜都陪佢睇波 姐係陪條女夜瞓冇乜所謂 但睇緊啲睇唔明嘅嘢真係幾痛苦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尤其係講到越位果陣 有日終於忍唔住問咩係越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果比佢笑到面都黃 問我點做男人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯有上來開個po 呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500a7e9aee9ba475298f26a77ebaf6c2b018ed0c","tid":717033,"uid":104422,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2fad149239f5a222ed45190c60d1a10af5baf65","tid":717033,"uid":26000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇巴打同我一樣 對足球冇乜興趣 所以做咁多年人都唔點留意足球<br />\n基本上可以話係對足球零認知<br />\n<br />\n反而條女呢 就好鍾意睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一來為𥄫仔 二來真係睇波<br />\n咁呢排世界杯 小弟原本都冇乜為意 但條女就上身咁款話要睇波<br />\n早個禮拜都陪佢睇波 姐係陪條女夜瞓冇乜所謂 但睇緊啲睇唔明嘅嘢真係幾痛苦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尤其係講到越位果陣 有日終於忍唔住問咩係越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果比佢笑到面都黃 問我